Driving the NKK Smartswitch.2. Graphics and text
Whether your message is one of workplace safety or world peace, the long nights
	of brooding over ways to tell the world are over. Part 1 described the
	basic interface to drive the Smartswitch. Part 2 adds the bells and
	whistles to allow both text and messages to be placed anywhere on the
	screen. It considers character generation, graphic generation and the
	user interface
